{
  "text": "I am Ra. I greet you in the love and the light of the Infinite Creator. Before we communicate by answer we shall correct an error which we have discovered in the transmission of our information to you. We have difficulty dealing with your time/space. There may again be errors of this type. Feel free to question us that we may recalculate in your time/space measurements. The error we have discovered concerns one of the arrivals of both the Orion group into your planetary sphere of influence and the corresponding arrival of emissaries of the Confederation. We gave dates of two six oh oh 2, 600 years for the Orion entry, two three oh oh 2, 300 for Confederation entry. This is incorrect. The recalculation indicates numbers three six oh oh 3, 600 for Orion entry, three three oh oh 3, 300 for Confederation entry. We communicate now.",
